Installation and uninstallation specification

Installation:
(1) run ./install
(2) input installation path(recommend defalut)
(3) choose create a .desktop file or not
(4) if chosen to create a .desktop file, offer an icon.ico file, 
    copy it to the software directory of package directory or give an absolute path
(5) finished

Uninstallation:
(1) run ./uninstall
(2) input uninstallation path
(3) finished
